However, there are several severe limitations to the simple approach of matching offers as just described.
(For example, it is not clear what the outcome should be when both parties offer to match the other"s donation.)
Examples of matching offers are: I will give x dollars for every dollar donated., or I will give x dollars if the total collected from other parties exceeds y.
